author_ssm: Stacey Flatt, with folder title listings written by Jessica Merliss.
unittitle_ssm: Research Collection on Gay Sexuality and Activism
abstract_ssm: An anonymous gay man living and working in New York during the 1970s through the 1990s accumulated this material related to gay sexuality, as well as gay rights and activism. This collection contains pornographic and erotic magazines, gay activism support and informational material, and news clippings.
